{"tid":1451591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[冷氣軍師請進] [五大訴求] 接住落黎開po回po可唔可以都加呢個footer落去？","createTime":"2019-08-11T19:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T19:37:28.000Z","uid":253363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2277bdaf7eed757cb31044cd1d36d4a0db5a6eb4","tid":1451591,"uid":253363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:33:59.000Z","msg":"呢場運動依家已經發展到和理非遊行集會同勇武行動愈來愈分不開<br />\n但隨住每次行動被捕、被打、被陰嘅手足愈來愈多 我地資本會逐漸減少<br />\n我地之後每次行動目的更加要聚焦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就算唔出去 冷氣軍師們你地都有野可以做</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就係唔好俾任何野洗走五大訴求呀！！！！！！</span></span><br />\n就算黑警幾仆街我地幾嬲都好<br />\n都要清晰記得行動目的！！！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">跪求大家以後開乜野po回乜野po都加返以下footer落去</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">===<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n務求所有人都記得呀！！！！！"},{"pid":"50cd44c8696536432bfa3b2234fd3d3c9a15e964","tid":1451591,"uid":253363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:34:20.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"53c70abc98ccb355b88150ba69faf5516f321ff6","tid":1451591,"uid":253363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:34:34.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"383bc079e34d8867684b41c79a00906c4ebf69a8","tid":1451591,"uid":253363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:34:52.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"603e920f0cd7cb0bb4915141e6750247132c296c","tid":1451591,"uid":253363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:37:06.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6db8f6682ccee942eb11cdc9ec38d51fdddd149e","tid":1451591,"uid":253363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/